                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing vanadium nitride by using mixed reducing gas",
                    "一种利用混合还原气制备氮化钒的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of metallurgy, in particular to a method for preparing vanadium nitride by using mixed reducing gas, which comprises the following steps: uniformly grinding vanadium trioxide, pressing to obtain a vanadium pentoxide tablet, putting the tablet into an electric furnace, and heating to room temperature; heating to 500-700 DEG C in a nitrogen atmosphere, introducing a mixed gas of methane, hydrogen and nitrogen, keeping the temperature for 20 minutes, continuously heating to 800-850 DEG C, and keeping the temperature for 20 minutes to obtain high-purity vanadium trioxide; then continuously heating to 1050-1150 DEG C, and keeping the temperature for 1-5 hours to obtain crude vanadium nitride; and stopping introducing the reducing gas, carrying out heat preservation for 0-4 hours at 1050-1150 DEG C in a nitrogen atmosphere, and then cooling to room temperature to obtain the high-quality vanadium nitride. According to the technical scheme, the vanadium nitride preparation process is low in temperature, short in time and easy to operate, and large-scale application of the vanadium nitride is achieved. And meanwhile, the obtained products are carbon monoxide and hydrogen which can be recycled, so that the carbon emission is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及冶金技术领域，尤其涉及一种利用混合还原气制备氮化钒的方法，该方法包括：将三氧化二钒研磨均匀按压制得五氧化二钒压片，压片放入电炉中，先在氮气气氛下升温至500‑700℃后通入甲烷、氢气、氮气混合气体并保温20min后继续升温至800‑850℃后保温20min制得高纯三氧化二钒；之后继续升温至1050℃‑1150℃并保温1‑5h后获得粗制氮化钒；停止通入还原性气体，仅在氮气气氛下于1050℃‑1150℃下保温0‑4h，随后冷却至室温，获得高品质氮化钒。本发明提及的技术方案中，氮化钒的制备过程温度低，时间短，操作简单，以实现其大规模应用。同时，其所得产物为一氧化碳、氢气，均可循环利用，有利于降低碳排放。"
                }
            ]
